.TH PAGESIZE 1 
.UC 5
.SH NAME
pagesize \- print system page size
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pagesize
.SH DESCRIPTION
.I Pagesize
prints the size of a page of memory in bytes, as
returned by
.IR getpagesize (2).
This program is useful in constructing portable
shell scripts.
.SH SEE ALSO
getpagesize(2)
